<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- hā qad̊ danā yaẘmu ạllĩqā
 bikaẘkabi ạlṣũb̊ḥi ạl̊munīr̊
 fālậna hīa sāʿaẗuⁿ
 linaf̊tadī ạl̊waq̊ta ạl̊qaṣīr̊

[V2]
 2- wal̊naṣ̊ḥu bitaʿaqũliⁿ
 lilṣãlawāti kulã ḥīn̊
 wal̊naʿ̊budi ạlrãbã maʿaⁿạ
 biqūãẗi ạlrũwḥi ạl̊muʿīn̊

[V3]
 3- waqab̊la hadẖā fal̊yakun̊
 ḥubuⁿ̃ sẖadīduⁿ fī ạl̊qulūb̊
 fāl̊ḥubũ yas̊turu ạl̊kẖaṭā
 wayaṣ̊faḥu ʿani ạldẖũnūb̊

[V4]
 4- waman̊ lahu maẘhibaẗuⁿ
 yakẖ̊dimu bihā kulã ḥīn̊
 ḥatãy̱ nakūna ạủmanā
 kawukalạʾa ṣāliḥīn̊

[V5]
 5- wakulũ man̊ yukatẖĩru
 fī ʿamali ạlrãbĩ ạltẖãmīn̊
 fabāṭilạaⁿ lạ yat̊ʿabu
 fī ạlrãbĩ yasūʿa ạlạảmīn̊</lyrics>
<title>hạ qd dnạ ywm ạllqạ</title>
</song>